reviewText: I originally only watched this movie because of Kris Wu but I genuinely enjoyed this movie. I do wish they would have done a little bit more with it as they had such a great idea they just didn't quite follow through on.
Wish this movie could be bought in the U.S. I would LOVE to see this movie because of Kris Wu, but I found out that the DVD can't be played in the U.S. and I don't own a Blueray machine.
Beautiful love story. Not a mere travelogue.
